{"word":"H5431 - סָאַן - çâʼan - saw-an' - Warrior","slug":"H5431","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">סָאַן</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>çâʼan"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>saw-an'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Warrior"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E1;&#x05D0;&#x05DF; - sa&#x0302;'an</b> - <i>saw-an'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>be miry</i>; used only as denominative from <a href=\"#/H5430\">H5430</a>; to <i>shoe</i>, that is, (active participle) a <i>soldier</i> shod: - warrior."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H5429\">H5429</a>, <a href=\"#/H5430\">H5430</a>"}]}